org.globus.ogsa.impl.base.providers.servicedata
Class TransientElement

java.lang.Object
  org.jdom.Element
      org.globus.ogsa.impl.base.providers.servicedata.TransientElement
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Cloneable, java.io.Serializable
public class TransientElement
extends org.jdom.Element

A soft-state XML Element class (JDOM-derived). Stores lifetime information as element attributes. Use this general-purpose class to build time-sensitive XML documents with the JDOM API.
